{"tid":2076796,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"外國Youtuber 推介 - James Jani","createTime":"2020-06-23T22:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:01:21.000Z","uid":10063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6177d34702347913a86034735fcc3358c27e472f","tid":2076796,"uid":10063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:12:11.000Z","msg":"最近多左留意youtube既野, 無意發現一位外國20歲既學術性youtuber - James Jani  <br />\n<br />\n<ins>小小簡介:</ins><br />\n-佢個Channel 只有8條片,每條片大約會用 60-80 個鐘整 <br />\n-雖然得8條片但1年已經有20萬訂閱 <br />\n-有2條片短短4個月有1百萬觀看(以youtube成長速度黎講好L勁,一條關於金錢,另一條關於最近市面成日見既FAKE GURU(今次推介既片,下面有講)<br />\n-佢既片用好多唔用既電影片,書籍,+埋自己既意見整成,最後用紀錄片(Documentary) 方式黎展示,每條大約~21分鐘<br />\n-話題主要係提出一D大多數人平常生活上唔會唸既野 (例如:唔好追逐金錢,唔好信哂市面自稱既專家教你既野,我地生活是否過度追求正面同自我發展(Self help),etc.<br />\n<br />\n今次推介呢位YOUTUBER既條片叫 <br />\nThe Rise of Fake Gurus: The Dark Truth Behind Making MILLIONS from Online Courses.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L9Gpr7PEnbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL9Gpr7PEnbs&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=fba1d0a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L9Gpr7PEnbs</a><br />\n<br />\n係我地生活中經常會見到一d自稱專家既人 (Gurus), 例如: Kevin David, Dan Lok, John Crestani<br />\n<br />\n而佢地通常會令你覺得你都有可能成為佢地一樣可以變到好有錢/財務自由/如何成為成功人士(但最後其實獲益最多係佢地自己既荷包)<br />\n<br />\n條片分為幾部分 (如何成為一個gurus)<br />\n1. Gurus 會有自己既主題,去教你一D你認為佢好專業既野,而通常呢d主題會勾起你既情感,例如對自己既無力感,對金錢既渴望以及生活不安感 (主題有: Sales, 網上搵錢,投資地產,bitcoin,etc)<br />\n<br />\n2.  Gurus 會搵專家寫犒比佢自己讀, 包裝到自己一個成功人士咁同埋拍片, 最後你會開始信佢好有經驗, 要你去試下聽下佢既教育<br />\n<br />\n3. (開始搵錢) Gurus 開始賣廣告,對象通常係年輕人, 會同d年輕人講夢想其實每個人都可以實現,唔洗再返份朝9晚5既工,好容易好快咁搵到6位數字, 由一個低收入士變到百萬富翁,  如果你都好想好似佢咁,要去Click佢既教學,link <br />\n<br />\n4. 最後呢d年輕人聽完會越來越相信佢講既野,向guru問更多未了解既問題,最後自己拎更多錢出黎去讀佢地d堂/買書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.  最後呢班gurus 只會越來越富有, 而比錢佢既學生只會比gurus話你唔夠努力or你未學夠<br />\n<br />\n自己睇完條片覺得上網學習其實係無問題既,但年輕人一定要有獨立思考能力去了解自己到底有無跟錯人學野,定其實只係比人呃緊錢自己唔知.<br />\n我自己覺得呢位youtuber 其他片會比到更多唔同既日常思考,我會推介埋<br />\nThe Untold Truth About Money: How to Build Wealth From Nothing.<br />\n有興趣自己去睇下吧<br />\n<br />\n_______________________<br />\n最後賣下廣告<br />\n小弟有個香港本土廣東話 恐怖遊戲YT Channel, 有興趣既黎支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/c/魚佬9CFamily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2F%E9%AD%9A%E4%BD%AC9CFamily&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=a173716f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/c/魚佬9CFamily</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjuSzXt.jpg&amp;h=e395ac1f&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"26bfbcd88976e978fb5bd934c7e374ebc9abaf42","tid":2076796,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8zMzPmalEm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8zMzPmalEm4&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=5ec85e7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8zMzPmalEm4</a><br />\n諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d402c5e60db19f4992ecd8682b86dc555fb52ff","tid":2076796,"uid":10063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26bfbcd88976e978fb5bd934c7e374ebc9abaf42","tid":2076796,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T22:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8zMzPmalEm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8zMzPmalEm4&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=5ec85e7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8zMzPmalEm4</a><br />\n諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T23:02:08.000Z","msg":"巴打點解會唸起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??  佢個樣似我？ 定係個外國youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"4d9ccd98ff0c755d13cb3e45776647da6b4c9917","tid":2076796,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dis